C702, C902, G502, K320i, K53Oi, K550i, K610i, K700i, K750i, K770i, K800i, S500i, V600i, V630i, V640i, V800, W300i, W550i, W580i, W595, W595s, W610i, W660i, W800i, W810i, W850i, W880i, W910i, Z520i, Z530i

